As a veteran of Peach, I had mixed expectations for this one. Many of their titles are stellar, but some can be prudish bores. This one falls in the middle because it has a lot of filler, but Teanna, Jessica and (I believe) Lana are awesome.

First of all, the DVD suffers from a dirth of girls; we see the same ones over and over. Except for Lana, who is in one scene and damn near steals the DVD with her luscious [...], bubble-b*tt and bedroom eyes. The other highlights are Teanna and Jessica (who appear in several scenes).

Teanna is a super hot Asian with amazing big [...], cute face and great bod. This is a good performance from her, but I've seen better. Jessica is really awesome here. With her lithe body and full [...], she puts on a show (in solo scenes and w/ Teanna) with great moves and a penchant for nice, open-legged, front & rear squats & spreads - WOW!

The other girls, though busty & fairly attrative, go thru the boring motions and offer little fun below the waist. Again, Lana was awesome, but I could have used more scenes (than one) and better close-ups.

Avoid this if you're not into exteriors (all). Best was probably a "medley" on a boat, where they cut between the girls.

A few hotties save this, but I've seen better from Peach.
The dvd Welcome to Peach Island was received in excellent condition.

What more can I ask for? .. this video has it all .. beautiful girls in skimpy bikins shot on exotic locations ..  I want to go to Peach Island. If you like this, check out "Wild Girls: Thailand" (ASIN: B000F6YVRW). Same formula, but with better music, and in Thailand! hot!

Whoa... These women are seriously hot(Well, most of them anyway).Teanna Kai and another young lady on the beach who appeared to be Pacific Asian Islander where the two most attractive.
